    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>One or two-piece garments designed to expose much of the body to the sun; worn for sunbathing or play by women and children.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
